---

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-warm">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-12" data-reveal>
      <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-secondary mb-4">What Gets Taken Off Your Plate</p>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-primary leading-tight">
        What you can hand off on Day 1
      </h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-base mt-4 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Not a list of capabilities. These are specific things I take over immediately so you stop doing them.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4" data-reveal-stagger>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-primary/[0.06]">
        <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-secondary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <svg class="w-4.5 h-4.5 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 17V7m0 10a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V7a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m0 10a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 7a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m0 10V7"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-primary text-sm mb-1">Board materials & governance</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-xs leading-relaxed">T-minus 3 week prep cycle. Committee briefings. Pre-meeting packages. Minutes. Action tracking.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-primary/[0.06]">
        <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-secondary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <svg class="w-4.5 h-4.5 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-primary text-sm mb-1">Investor correspondence & CRM</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-xs leading-relaxed">Stakeholder tracking. Quarterly updates. Ad-hoc requests. Response time under 24 hours.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-primary/[0.06]">
        <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-secondary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <svg class="w-4.5 h-4.5 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-primary text-sm mb-1">Calendar architecture & meeting prep</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-xs leading-relaxed">Priority-structured weeks. Briefing notes. Agendas. Follow-ups tracked and assigned.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-primary/[0.06]">
        <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-secondary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <svg class="w-4.5 h-4.5 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-primary text-sm mb-1">Travel logistics</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-xs leading-relaxed">Domestic and international. Door-to-door itineraries. Backup options. Visa and currency notes.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-primary/[0.06]">
        <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-secondary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <svg class="w-4.5 h-4.5 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-primary text-sm mb-1">Executive onboarding playbooks</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-xs leading-relaxed">90-day plans. Stakeholder maps. Decision-rights matrices. New leaders productive from week one.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-primary/[0.06]">
        <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-secondary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <svg class="w-4.5 h-4.5 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 8h10M7 12h4m1 8l-4-4H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-3l-4 4z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-primary text-sm mb-1">Internal comms & drafting</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-xs leading-relaxed">All-hands announcements. Leadership updates. Sensitive communications. Right tone, right audience.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-primary/[0.06]">
        <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-secondary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <svg class="w-4.5 h-4.5 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-primary text-sm mb-1">Cross-functional project coordination</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-xs leading-relaxed">Bridging legal, finance, ops, and comms. Nothing falls between teams.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-primary/[0.06]">
        <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-secondary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <svg class="w-4.5 h-4.5 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-primary text-sm mb-1">Expense & vendor management</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-xs leading-relaxed">Receipt tracking. Vendor negotiations. Budget monitoring. Clean documentation.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-primary/[0.06]">
        <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-secondary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <svg class="w-4.5 h-4.5 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-primary text-sm mb-1">AI-powered research & briefing</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-xs leading-relaxed">Using Claude and Perplexity since 2024. Stakeholder research. Draft preparation. 40% faster than manual.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
